"""
rr2_nmf_gui_ver4_4_full_eds.py

Residual-aware recursive rank-k NMF GUI for EELS/EDS spectral-imaging data.

v4.4 integrated features
------------------------
1. Raw data view with ROI and energy-axis support.
2. Conventional NMF comparison.
3. Residual-aware recursive NMF tree.
   - Default residual mode: redistribute_equal
   - Default init: random
   - Tree node layout:
       [ C0 image ] [ C1 image ]
       [ H0 spec  ] [ H1 spec  ]
       [      Residual map      ]
       [   Residual spectrum    ]
4. Background correction.
   - Power-law background: I(E)=A*E^(-r)
   - r fitted from selected spatial ROI and selected energy window.
   - pixel-wise amplitude A_p applied to full cube.
5. rr-NMF component recombination.
   - Select arbitrary D/N/C components.
   - Sum W_i H_i into synthetic dataset.
   - Preview and export NPZ.
6. EELS/EDS interpretation support databases.
7. EDS Analysis tab.
   - Select raw / rr-NMF / conventional-NMF spectra.
   - Select elements using compact periodic-table buttons or presets.
   - Detect peaks and match to major/minor X-ray lines.
   - Overlay X-ray lines and export/use match table.

Install
-------
pip install numpy pandas scikit-learn matplotlib PyQt5

Optional loaders
----------------
pip install hyperspy exspy rosettasciio
"""

